snippet.title: 【GRAND FANTASIA : ORIGIN】Relive the most classic MMORPG adventure!
snippet.description:
《GRAND FANTASIA - ORIGIN》Classic MMORPG returns with innovation, creating legends once more!

▼Play NOW:
https://xleg.cc/xX48WgS
▼Steam :
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3010230/Grand_Fantasia__ORIGIN/

Grand Fantasia is an anime-style MMORPG with stunning landscapes along with a wealth of PVP and PVE features. Embark on a fantasy adventure with your sprites. 
Become a sprite messenger in the fantasy world of Grand Fantasia!

#grandfantasia"
